      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software must be under configuration management with documented test suite achieving ≥90% coverage of hemolysis-relevant code paths.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver is under version control but formal test suite coverage is undocumented. Configuration management records are incomplete for the hemolysis damage model subroutine. Achieved level 2 falls short of required level 4 for MRL 5."
