      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy testing must confirm theoretical convergence rate for all governing equations including the hemolysis transport equation.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy testing was performed for momentum and continuity equations but not for the hemolysis scalar transport equation. Convergence rate confirmed at 1.8 (expected 2.0) for flow variables only. Achieved level 2 is insufficient for MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
