      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must be conducted on the same pump geometry under COU flow-speed conditions or formally justified analogues.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, not the actual VAD device geometry. Geometric similarity is partial; the impeller blade angle differs by 12 degrees from the COU device. Relevance gap is not formally quantified."
    },
