      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent simulation replication by a second analyst must confirm reproducibility of hemolysis predictions within 5%.",
      "rationale": "No independent replication study was conducted. A single analyst team performed all simulations. Use error is flagged as an epistemic gap; factor not formally assessed at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
