      "acceptanceCriteria": "The hemolysis damage model form must be justified against mechanistic understanding with sensitivity analysis documenting model form uncertainty contribution.",
      "rationale": "The power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model was selected without documented justification over alternative mechanistic models. No model form uncertainty analysis was conducted. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
