      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters must have documented sources with uncertainty characterization; Monte Carlo sampling must cover the full COU operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed over inlet boundary conditions. However, material property inputs (blood viscosity, red cell mechanical properties) were treated as deterministic. Input uncertainty characterization is incomplete for MRL 5 requirements."
