    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain as epistemic gaps. Despite the gaps, the package is accepted for submission pending remediation plan. The mesh independence verification activity was declared as a structured study supporting discretization error assessment.",
